dct_title_s: Kaisei Mie-ken gunson meisaizu zen; Kamai Yūjirō.
dct_description_sm: Oriented with north to the upper right. Mounted cover title. Title on map: Kaisei Mie-ken gunson meisaizu. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Relief shown by hachures. 4 sheets joined. Includes text on districts, preface and legend. 1 map: col.; 49 x 76 cm., folded in cover 13 x 13 cm.
